snippet.title: Moley Christmas Walkthrough, ZX Spectrum
snippet.description:
A walkthrough of the ZX Spectrum game, Moley Christmas. This mini Monty Mole game was on a cover tape for Your Sinclair magazine. From the recording originally sent to http://www.rzxarchive.co.uk/

#ZXSpectrum #RetroGaming #Walkthrough
